@@TJvFormPlacement.Form
Summary
  Provides access to the form which placement is controlled by the component.
Description
  Use Form to access the form - the owner of this component - which placement is controlled by this
  component.

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvFormPlacement.IsActive
Summary
  Indicates whether Active is set to true and an application storage component is specified.
Description
  IsActive indicates whether the form storage component is active.
Return value
