@@TJvWinMinMaxInfo
Summary
  Contains information about a window's maximized size and position and its minimum and maximum
  tracking size.
Description
  TJvWinMinMaxInfo is a wrapper for the windows MINMAXINFO structure. It contains the metrics of a
  specific form.

