@@TJvFormStorage.StoredPropsPath
Summary
  The path to add before the name of any item of StoredProps
Description
  If there are items of StoredProps and StoredValues that have the same name, the generated file will
  be invalid and will not be readable. To avoid this, set this property and/or StoredValuesPath to a
  non empty value.
